data.description: Experience the ultimate Alaskan lifestyle with this captivating lakefront home on Cheri Lake. This idyllic 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home, boasting 140 ft of exclusive lakefront, is a haven of rustic elegance and serene beauty. Nestled in a private, quiet location, the property offers stunning, sunny lake views and a direct connection to the tranquility of Cheri Lake.Enjoy your own slice of paradise with a floating dock and paddleboat included. Located on a spacious 1.54-acre lot, this secluded retreat, surrounded mostly by State Land, with no public lake access, offers peace and privacy.  Immerse in the Alaskan dream with this home's authentic charm. Newer (2011) kitchen, bedroom, bathroom and laundry room provide 600 sq ft additional living space, blending modern comfort with rustic appeal. Homesteading Ready: Features a greenhouse and three large sheds perfect for sustainable living. Possibilities for float plane access. Ideal for family gatherings, outdoor adventures, and creating lasting memories. Peace of mind with a seller-paid HSA home warranty. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to own a piece of Alaskan paradise, a perfect blend of seclusion, rustic charm, and modern amenities. Secure your dream lakefront home today!
